		<br />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"><span style="font-size: large;"><strong><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">“</span></strong><strong>子规声中烟如雨</strong><strong><span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">”</span></strong><strong>专场音乐会</strong></span><strong> </strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">时间：<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">2013</span>年<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">4</span>月<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19</span>日<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">  </span>晚<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">19:30</span></span> </p>
 
<p> <span style="font-family: Times New Roman; color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">一、女声独唱《人间第一情》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                               </span>易茗词 刘青曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                        《家和万事兴》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                           石顺义、郁钧剑</span>词 刘青曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     演唱：亓泓几</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">二、扬琴独奏《林冲夜奔》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                        </span>项祖华编曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                    演奏：袁可（香港龙音杯器乐大赛金奖）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">三、男声独唱《鸿雁》<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">                                                                     </span>根据蒙古民歌改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                         《父亲的草原母亲的河》                    <span style="font-family: Times New Roman;">               </span>席慕容词<span style="font-family: Times New Roman;"> </span>乌兰托噶曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     演唱：谢宇鹏</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">四、中胡独奏《草原上》                                                                                 刘明源曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                     演奏：王雪飞</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">五、女高音独唱《祖国我永远祝福你》                                                云剑词 印青曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                            《我的深情为你守候》                                            陈道斌词 栾凯曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                    演唱：郑丽红</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">六、女声二重唱《我们的生活充满阳光》                          集体作词 吕远、唐诃曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                                 演唱：郑丽红 亓泓几</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">七、二胡独奏《江河水》                                          根据东北民间乐曲黄海怀移植</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                 演奏：金玥（文化部优秀剧目展演获奖者、香港龙音杯器乐大赛金奖）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">八、女中音独唱《草原夜色美》                                                    白洁词  王和声曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                              《我爱你中国》                                                  翟宗词  郑秋枫曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                              《今夜无眠》                                                      朱海词  孟卫东曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                             演唱：宋伶俐（国家一级演员）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">九、大提琴独奏《天鹅》                                                                                 圣桑曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                  演奏：田维扬（法国布列斯特国际艺术节获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十、女声独唱《孝敬父母》                                                             车行词 戚建波曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                         《美丽中国》                                                       李俊伟词  雷远生曲</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                 演唱：贾静思（第六届东方旋律国际音乐节获奖者）</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">十一、弦乐四重奏《自由探戈》                          <span style="font-size: medium;">        </span> 皮亚佐拉曲 罗麦朔移植改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                《炫动》                                                       <span style="font-size: medium;">高韶青</span>曲 罗麦朔改编</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;">                                 演奏：金玥 宋雷 王雪飞 田维扬</span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<p style="padding-left: 30px;"><span style="color: #000000; font-size: small;">注：曲目如有变动，请以演出当日为准。                                                【2013-A-007】</span></p>		</div>

		
			
